    <sectiondef kind="user-defined">
      <header>PWM period set helpers</header>
      <description><para>The period cell in the PWM specifier needs to be provided in nanoseconds.</para>
<para>However, in some applications it is more convenient to use another scale. </para>
</description>
      <member refid="group__pwm__interface_1ga17f20d628bcc81d5023c39e4cdfad405" kind="define"><name>PWM_NSEC</name></member>
